In part 1, we made sure every request carried a stable `CorrelationId` through logs and outbound HTTP calls. That solved log search. Now we solve the next problem: aligning that id with distributed traces so one incident can be explored from either side.

This post uses the same field-maintenance domain: Dispatcher UI -> Work Orders API -> Inventory API -> Routing API.

